  "keyFeatures": [
    "High-quality PDF rendering via PDFium (Docnet.Core)",
    "Inline text editing with font matching against the original document",
    "Text boxes, freehand drawing, and highlight overlays with adjustable color, size, and opacity",
    "Draw and save reusable signatures — click to place on any page",
    "Full-text search with result highlighting",
    "Drag-select to copy text from PDF pages",
    "Merge multiple PDFs and split out selected pages",
    "Drag-and-drop page reordering",
    "Print with annotations flattened into the output",
    "Single portable EXE (~6 MB), no installer, no runtime, no admin rights, no telemetry"
